# Vanilla Framework compliance

Use [Vanilla Framework](https://vanillaframework.io/) exactly as Canonical production sites do ([canonical.com](https://github.com/canonical/canonical.com), [snapcraft.io](https://github.com/canonical/snapcraft.io)).

## SCSS build (required)

```scss
// 1. Override settings BEFORE importing Vanilla
$color-brand: #…;
$color-accent: $color-brand;

// 2. Import framework (requires --load-path=node_modules on sass CLI)
@import "vanilla-framework";

// 3. Emit CSS — full site OR cherry-picked patterns
@include vanilla; // canonical.com & snapcraft.io default
// OR for small surfaces: @include vf-base; @include vf-p-grid; … (see snapcraft styles-embedded.scss)
```

Build command pattern: `sass … --load-path=node_modules --style=compressed`

Custom styles live in `_pattern_*.scss` partials: `@import` then `@include project-name`, using Vanilla mixins (`vf-animation`, `vf-icon-*`, `vf-theme-dark`) — never reimplement components.

## HTML layout (required)

- `body` → `class="l-site"` (optionally `is-paper` theme)
- Skip link: `<a href="#main-content" class="u-off-screen">Skip to main content</a>`
- Navigation: `header#navigation` with `p-navigation--sliding is-dark`, inner `p-navigation__row--25-75`, `p-navigation__tagged-logo`, mobile `p-navigation__toggle--open`
- Main: `id="main-content"` wrapped in `section.p-strip` + inner `div.u-fixed-width`
- Grid: `p-grid` / `p-grid__cell--span-*` / `p-grid__cell--small-span-4` (always set small-span for mobile)
- Notifications: `p-notification--*` + `p-notification__content` + `u-hide` to toggle
- Utilities: `u-fixed-width`, `u-hide`, `u-no-padding--top`, `p-heading--4` — not inline styles

## Forbidden

- Bootstrap, Tailwind, or other CSS frameworks
- Inline `style=` for layout/spacing (use `p-strip`, `u-*`, `p-section--*`)
- Overriding Vanilla component rules without a tracked Vanilla issue
- Importing Vanilla without `--load-path=node_modules`

## JS

- Prefer Vanilla packaged modules (`vanilla-framework/templates/static/js/tabs.js`) for tabs/accordions
- Navigation toggle: follow snapcraft `_header.html` + listeners pattern; do not invent new nav markup
